1. using self-signed certificates for https
2. Not resolved https apps issues

Self-Signed Certificates

``
sudo openssl req -x509 -nodes -days 365 -newkey rsa:2048 -keyout /etc/ssl/private/selfsigned.key -out /etc/ssl/certs/selfsigned.crt
``

For local should add to etc/hosts 
``
<REMOTE_SERVER_PUBLIC_IP> gitea.xwing.pn glances.xwing.pn portainer.xwing.pn uptime.xwing.pn adguard.xwing.pn navidrome.xwing.pn mongo.xwing.pn postgres.xwing.pn nextcloud.xwing.pn
``